2001-3297 (La. 10/25/02)

STATE ex rel. Leonard FARVE v. STATE of Louisiana. No. 2001-KH-3297. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re Farve, Leonard; — Plaintiff; Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of Jefferson, 24th Judicial District Court Div. M, Nos. 94-4203, 94-4204, 94-4280; to the Court of Appeal, Fifth Circuit, No. 01-KH-98.

Denied. La.C.Cr.P. art. 930.8; State ex rel. Glover v. State, 93-2330 (La.9/5/95), 660 So.2d 1189; State v. Parker, 98-0256 (La.5/8/98), 711 So.2d 694.
